data.description: Welcome to 25 Gallie Cut, where luxury living meets unparalleled comfort. This exquisite residence boasts six bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, including a convenient full bedroom and bathroom downstairs, perfect for guests or multi-generational living. Step outside onto the screened-in patio and into the expansive fenced yard, where privacy and serenity await. The centerpiece of the outdoor oasis is the brand-new Swimspa, offering the ultimate relaxation experience with a warranty attached for peace of mind. Whether you're hosting gatherings with loved ones or enjoying quiet moments of solitude, 25 Gallie Cut offers the perfect blend of elegance, convenience, and outdoor indulgence.
